      "description": "Ba3PbO (antiperovskite, mp-29242) vs BaBiO3 (perovskite, mp-545783): identical bond topology with inverted cation/anion roles.  The role-swap trial in match_nodes_ged should detect the perovskite \u2194 antiperovskite equivalence and return cost \u2248 0.  Cation/anion mapping after swap: Ba (antiperov anion) \u2194 O (perov anion) is the X-site; Pb (antiperov cation X-site) \u2194 Ba (perov A-site); O (antiperov B-site) \u2194 Bi (perov B-site).",
